 h\u00fat h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/CLB-HAGL-bat-ngo-vuon-len-dan-dau-tai-chau-A-ve-suc-hut-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>CLB HAGL d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u1ec1 l\u01b0\u1ee3t xem tr\u00ean Youtube</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo m\u1ed9t th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea c\u1ee7a&nbsp;Depor&amp;Finanzas v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1, CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u \u00c1 trong th\u00e1ng 7 khi thu h\u00fat \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2,75 tri\u1ec7u l\u01b0\u1ee3t xem tr\u00ean Youtube. Con s\u1ed1 kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ecf xa \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00e1m \u0111u\u1ed5i Buriram (ch\u1ec9 h\u01a1n 2,2 tri\u1ec7u).</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1edf d\u0129 HAGL &lsquo;v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed1i&rsquo; t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c1 b\u1edfi h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00e0 y\u00eau th\u00edch t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u C\u0110V n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n bi\u1ebft t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u00e0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng thi \u0111\u1ea5u. Vi\u1ec7c HAGL \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ebfn m\u1ed9 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u cho th\u1ea5y NHM ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd ng\u1eebng quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1eb9p.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, vi\u1ec7c v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u \u00c1 c\u1ee7a HAGL c\u0169ng kh\u00e1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd b\u1edfi trong th\u00e1ng v\u1eeba qua, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng khi ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng 1, ho\u00e0 1 v\u00e0 thua \u0111\u1ebfn 2&nbsp;tr\u1eadn. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3, giai \u0111o\u1ea1n n\u00e0y c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i &ldquo;c\u1ea1nh tranh&rdquo; g\u1eaft gao v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch World Cup \u0111\u1ea7y s\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u \u0111\u00e1ng m\u1eebng cho nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng, ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a HAGL nh\u1eefng n\u0103m \u0111\u00e3 qua.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee9 hai v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong t\u1ed1p 10 l\u00e0 CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 4 v\u1edbi h\u01a1n 1,6 tri\u1ec7u l\u01b0\u1ee3t xem. X\u1ebfp tr\u00ean H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i l\u00e0 Persib Bandung, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Indonesia.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-tin-tuong-hoc-tro-se-tao-nen-su-khac-biet-tai-olympic-viet-nam-168-192384.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/hlv-hagl-tin-tuong-hoc-tro-se-tao-nen-su-khac-biet-tai-olympic-viet-nam.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-tin-tuong-hoc-tro-se-tao-nen-su-khac-biet-tai-olympic-viet-nam-168-192384.html\">HLV HAGL tin t\u01b0\u1edfng h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t t\u1ea1i Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t chia s\u1ebb m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV HAGL \u00f4ng D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t t\u1ea1i ASIAD s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1922","checkdouble":"192596"},{"date":"06:17 03/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Paris vs Nancy 01h00 ng\u00e0y 4/8 (H\u1ea1ng 2 Ph\u00e1p 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/nhan-dinh-paris-vs-nancy-01h00-ngay-48-hang-2-phap-201819.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Paris vs Nancy l\u00fac 01h00 ng\u00e0y 4/8 (V\u00f2ng 2 gi\u1ea3i H\u1ea1ng 2 Ph\u00e1p Ligue 2 2018/19): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Paris vs Nancy 01h00 ng\u00e0y 48 H\u1ea1ng 2 Ph\u00e1p 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Paris vs Nancy 01h00 ng\u00e0y 48 H\u1ea1ng 2 Ph\u00e1p 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/Paris-FC-vs-Nancy.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Paris vs Nancy</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span>Paris vs Nancy: 0-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>\u1ede v\u00f2ng m\u1edf m\u00e0n gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng 2 Ph\u00e1p 2018/19, c\u1ea3 Paris FC v\u00e0 Nancy \u0111\u1ec1u thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t. Trong khi Paris ch\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ajaccio th\u00ec Nancy l\u1ea1i thua t\u00e2n binh Beziers 0-2 ngay t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. T\u00ednh c\u1ea3 tour du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8, Nancy ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 1/5 tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nParis FC s\u1edf h\u1eefu l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 n\u00ean trong th\u1ebf c\u1eeda d\u01b0\u1edbi, h\u1ecd th\u01b0\u1eddng thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Nh\u01b0ng khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i hay g\u00e2y ra th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn, \u0111\u00fang l\u00e0 Nancy m\u1edbi thua t\u00e2n binh Beziers song h\u00f4m \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0, h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i trong th\u1ebf 10 ng\u01b0\u1eddi.\u00a0Nancy thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t v\u00ec thi\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean n\u1ebfu ph\u1ea3i \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00e1p ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, Nancy v\u1eabn l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1ng ng\u1ea1i v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o. 2 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Didier Tholot t\u1eebng mang v\u1ec1 ni\u1ec1m vui theo TLCA khi b\u1ecb x\u1ebfp \u1edf c\u1eeda d\u01b0\u1edbi. Nancy h\u1eb3n kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n n\u1ebfm th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 2 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp n\u00ean c\u00f3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00eam nay. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i nh\u01b0 Paris FC, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Didier Tholot ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00c0NH T\u00cdCH \u0110\u1ed0I \u0110\u1ea6U<br>\r\n- Paris to\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong 2 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Nancy g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng 2 Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH D\u1ef0 KI\u1ebeN<br>\r\n+ Paris FC (4-1-4-1): Demarconnay - Rufli, Kante, Bong, Delaine - Akichi - Karramoko, Bougrine, Mandouki, Saint-Louis - Mamilonne.<br>\r\n+ Nancy (4-4-2): Assembe - Abergel, Seka, Diagne, Nery - Marchetti, Clement, Da Cruz, Robic - Dale, Koura.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1921","checkdouble":"192597"},{"date":"06:37 03/08","title":"N\u00f3ng: Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chia tay M.U","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/nong-them-mot-cau-thu-chia-tay-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i Joel Pereira \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay M.U \u0111\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Vitoria Setubal theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n.</h2><h2>Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chia tay M.U</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi Anh x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i Joel Pereira s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean ti\u1ebfp theo chia tay \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford trong h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00edch \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a anh s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, Vitoria Setubal.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pereira t\u1eebng l\u00e0 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a l\u00f2 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb Neuch\u00e2tel Xamax t\u1ea1i Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi gia nh\u1eadp Man United v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2012. Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00f4n l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i 1 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf t\u1eeb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2015/16 tuy nhi\u00ean t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn nay, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 22 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y m\u1edbi thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 3 tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Joel Pereira chia tay MU theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Joel Pereira chia tay MU theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/7/9/Thu-mon-Joel-Pereira-chia-tay-MU-theo-dang-cho-muon-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Joel Pereira chia tay M.U d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fd do m\u00e0 M.U mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp cho Joel Pereira \u0111i h\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7c. \u1ede hai m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2015/16 v\u00e0 2016/17, ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c M.U cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u1ea1ng d\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u01b0 Rochdale\u00a0hay Belenenses song s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Joel Pereira c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i \u1edf con s\u1ed1 10 trong m\u1ed7i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. V\u00ec th\u1ebf M.U kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u00e1ch n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n Joel Pereira \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c Pereira ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i c\u0169ng l\u00e0 do M.U v\u1eeba chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u00e2n binh Grant. Anh s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong 3 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u2018ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u1ec7n\u2019 David De Gea v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u Romero.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn kh\u00e1c, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 M.U Paul Pogba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c g\u1eb7p v\u1edbi Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a Barca, Eric Abidal trong k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 t\u1ea1i Beverly Hills, M\u1ef9. Cu\u1ed9c g\u1eb7p n\u00e0y nh\u1eb1m b\u00e0n th\u1ea3o v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Barca. L\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Nou Camp \u0111ang coi Pogba l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1ed1 1 sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu Pogba mu\u1ed1n, Mourinho c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 anh ra \u0111i v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 sung m\u1ed9t nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay th\u1ebf. Theo m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ngu\u1ed3n tin, Mourinho mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed5i Pogba \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y Ivan Rakitic.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1920","checkdouble":"192598"},{"date":"06:32 03/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Reading vs Derby County 02h00 ng\u00e0y 4/8 (H\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Anh 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/nhan-dinh-reading-vs-derby-county-02h00-ngay-48-hang-nhat-anh-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay Reading vs Derby County l\u00fac 02h00 ng\u00e0y 4/8 (V\u00f2ng 1 gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t Anh Championship 2018/19): \u00dd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Reading vs Derby County 02h00 ng\u00e0y 48 H\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Reading vs Derby County 02h00 ng\u00e0y 48 H\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/Reading-vs-Derby-County.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Reading vs Derby County</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span>Reading vs Derby County: 1-2</span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Reading \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i v\u00f4 s\u1ed1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh 44 \u0111i\u1ec3m, v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00edch th\u1ee9 20 chung cu\u1ed9c v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 h\u01a1n v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m so v\u1edbi nh\u00f3m xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, Reading c\u1ea7n 1 cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea3i t\u1ed5 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018-19. Tuy nhi\u00ean, do h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf v\u1ec1 ng\u00e2n s\u00e1ch, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Paul Clement ch\u1ec9 b\u1ed5 sung \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0i t\u00e2n binh mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed nh\u01b0 David Meyler (Hull) hay John O'Shea (Sunderland).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 1 trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t trong tour du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 2018 v\u1eeba qua. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, trong 6 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Paul Clement kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 n\u1ed5i 1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng (thua 3).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, Derby County \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng 3/4 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8. V\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1, d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ed5 sung \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd song The Rams \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 ch\u1ee7 ch\u1ed1t \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong nh\u00f3m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 play-off th\u0103ng h\u1ea1ng m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc (Top 6). Quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n, Derby County \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Frank Lampard v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong tour du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 2018 cho th\u1ea5y Derby County \u0111ang \u0111i \u0111\u00fang h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Lampard. Derby County c\u00f2n c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 cho tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi 2018/19. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, Reading l\u1ea1i m\u1ea5t t\u1edbi 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 \u00e1n treo gi\u00f2. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nDerby County \u0111ang th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV Lampard khi 4/5 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a The Rams \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 3 b\u00e0n. Ngo\u00e0i ra, c\u1ea3 3 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y gi\u1eefa 2 \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169ng c\u00f3 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00c0NH T\u00cdCH \u0110\u1ed0I \u0110\u1ea6U<br>\r\n- Reading ch\u1ec9 thua 3/15 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Derby County g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t Anh (th\u1eafng 7, h\u00f2a, 5, thua 3).<br>\r\n- C\u1ea3 3 cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t gi\u1eefa 2 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 5 b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n- Derby County b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong 6 chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Derby County (th\u1eafng 2, h\u00f2a 4).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00d4NG TIN L\u1ef0C L\u01af\u1ee2NG<br>\r\n- Reading: V\u1eafng Leandro Bacuna, Garath McCleary, Callum Harriott, Jordan Obita (ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng) v\u00e0 Tyler Blackett (treo gi\u00f2); Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Omar Richards c\u00f2n b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf.<br>\r\n- Derby County: V\u1eafng Chris Martin (ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng); Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Matej Vydra v\u00e0 Ikechi Anya c\u00f2n b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf.</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1919","checkdouble":"192599"},{"date":"06:52 03/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Palestine (19h30 ng\u00e0y 3/8): Ch\u1edd c\u01a1n m\u01b0a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/3/nhan-dinh-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-palestine-19h30-ngay-038-cho-con-mua-ban-thang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea3 hai \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Palestine \u0111\u1ec1u tung ra \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t c\u01a1n m\u01b0a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong 90 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.</h2><h2>U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u2013 c\u1ef1 t\u1eadp d\u01b0\u1ee3t quan tr\u1ecdng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018, VFF ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p c\u00f9ng nh\u00e0 t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3 Vinaphone \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018, quy t\u1ee5 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c. \u0110\u00e2y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t d\u1ecbp kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u1eed l\u1eeda v\u00e0 ch\u1ee9ng minh n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c trong m\u1eaft HLV Park Hang Seo v\u00e0 ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng t\u1eeb VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y h\u01a1n n\u1eeda n\u0103m, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn NHM r\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p U23 Palestine. Th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng, c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 tin v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd\u00a0kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Palestine, 19h30 ng\u00e0y 038 Ch\u1edd m\u1ed9t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Palestine, 19h30 ng\u00e0y 038 Ch\u1edd m\u1ed9t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/4/Nhan-dinh-U23-Viet-Nam-vs-U23-Palestine,-19h30-ngay-038-Cho-mot-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Palestine:\u00a0Ch\u1edd c\u01a1n m\u01b0a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee9 nh\u1ea5t, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c v\u1edbi 100% quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m nh\u1eb1m h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf t\u1edbi m\u1ee9c th\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00ednh HLV Park Hang Seo th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 cho bi\u1ebft d\u00f9 r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ec1u l\u00f2ng NHM, nh\u01b0ng gi\u1ea3i T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01a1n thu\u1ea9n ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 cho ASIAD v\u00e0 xa h\u01a1n l\u00e0 AFF Cup v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m.\u00a0<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Do \u0111\u00f3, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n k\u1ef3 t\u00edch gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u00e1 qu\u00e2n ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018. Do \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 nghi\u1ec7m n\u00ean c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi c\u00e1c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01a1n tru khi th\u1ea7y Park s\u1ebd trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng th\u1ebf, v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u00e0 c\u1ea1nh tranh huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ea1i ASIAD, HLV Park Hang Seo v\u00e0 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng d\u1ea1i g\u00ec bung h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 l\u1ed9 b\u00e0i cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng ASIAD. Thay v\u00ec \u0111\u00e1 \u2018ch\u1ebft b\u1ecf\u2019 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u00e0 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn \u1edf gi\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0103n \u00fd, hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 l\u1ea1c quan nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">G\u1eb7p U23 Palestine, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 hai U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y trong n\u0103m nay. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 h\u00f2a 1-1 trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 t\u1ea1i Trung Qu\u1ed1c. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">U23 Palestine \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu d\u00e0n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1t c\u00f9ng l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t, gi\u00e0u t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9.\u00a0V\u00ec th\u1ebf \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t thu\u1ed1c th\u1eed li\u1ec1u cao \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 h\u1ebft kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-palestine-noi-gi-ve-olympic-viet-nam-168-192552.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/hlv-palestine-noi-gi-ve-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-palestine-noi-gi-ve-olympic-viet-nam-168-192552.html\">HLV Palestine n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</span><br>\r\nV\u1ecb HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng U23 Palestine \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1ec1 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng c\u00fap Vinaphone 2018 s\u00e1ng 2/8.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>U23 Palestine \u2013 th\u1ebf l\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y \u00c1<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, U23 Palestine v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 kh\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. \u1ede v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Palestine \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-1, bu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh CHDCND Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean ph\u1ea3i chia \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi h\u1ea1 Th\u00e1i Lan v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1eadm 5-1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p U23 Qatar, d\u00f9 b\u1ecb d\u1eabn v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t 3 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i thi\u1ebfu ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eeb ph\u00fat 77 nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23 Palestine c\u00f3 m\u00e0n r\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111u\u1ed5i k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh v\u1edbi U23 Qatar, khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a World Cup 2022 ph\u1ea3i h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 m\u1edbi gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng s\u00e1t n\u00fat 3-2.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00f3, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i, U23 Palestine s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm v\u1edbi \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng. T\u1edbi v\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, HLV Sandouqa c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 mang theo nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Theo \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1, l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a U23 Palestine sang Vi\u1ec7t Nam r\u1ea5t h\u00f9ng h\u1eadu v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Palestine (19h30 ng\u00e0y 38) Ch\u1edd c\u01a1n m\u01b0a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Palestine (19h30 ng\u00e0y 38) Ch\u1edd c\u01a1n m\u01b0a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/Nhan-dinh-U23-Viet-Nam-vs-U23-Palestine-(19h30-ngay-38)-Cho-con-mua-ban-thang-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>U23 Palestine t\u1eebng thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u1eeba qua</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i c\u00e1c g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 nh\u01b0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Abuaker, Fahkouri, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Alashhab, Farawi, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Abuwada, Fannoun, Dabbagh, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Yousef, Qymbor\u2026, h\u1ecd c\u00f2n c\u00f3 2 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n l\u00e0 Termanini (CLB Eskilstuna) v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 El-Kayed (Prespa Birlik). V\u1edbi d\u00e0n tinh binh \u1ea5y, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y \u00c1 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 l\u00ed do g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i e ng\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">U23 Palestine \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 \u1edf l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, gi\u00e0u s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u00f9ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t. Tuy nhi\u00ean, U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh ri\u00eang \u1edf k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 \u0103n \u00fd khi nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh c\u00f9ng nhau t\u1eeb c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Do \u0111\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f9ng \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 HLV hai \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd tung nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb v\u00e0o s\u00e2n. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n: U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 3-2 U23 Palestine</strong><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:</strong><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p>U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam: V\u0103n L\u00e2m; V\u0103n Thanh, Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, Duy M\u1ea1nh, V\u0103n H\u1eadu, H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c, Quang H\u1ea3i, Anh \u0110\u1ee9c. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">U23 Palestine: Fahkouri; Alashhab, Farawi, Qatmish, Termanini, Abuwada, Fannoun, El-Kayed, Dabbagh, Yousef, Qymbor.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-tuyen-bo-manh-me-truoc-giai-giao-huu-quoc-te-2018-168-192542.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/hlv-park-hang-seo-tuyen-bo-manh-me-truoc-giai-giao-huu-quoc-te-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-tuyen-bo-manh-me-truoc-giai-giao-huu-quoc-te-2018-168-192542.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018</span><br>\r\nPh\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf c\u00fap Vinaphone 2018, HLV Park Hang Seo cho bi\u1ebft ...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng - C\u00fap Vinaphone 2018:</strong><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em><strong>Th\u1ee9 S\u00e1u, ng\u00e0y 3/8/2018:</strong></em><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">16h30:\u00a0Uzbekistan vs Oman\u00a0(Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp VTV6, B\u0110TV, THVL2)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">19h30: U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam - Palestine (Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp VTV6, B\u0110TV, THVL2)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em><strong>Ch\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt, ng\u00e0y 5/8/2018</strong></em><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">16h30: Uzbekistan vs Palestine\u00a0(Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp VTV5, B\u0110TV, THVL2)<br>\r\n19h30: U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Oman\u00a0(Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp VTV5, B\u0110TV, THVL2)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em><strong>Th\u1ee9 Ba, ng\u00e0y 7/8/2018</strong></em><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">16h30: Oman vs Palestine (Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp VTV6, B\u0110TV, THVL2)<br>\r\n19h30: U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Uzbekistan (Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp VTV6, B\u0110TV, THVL2)<span style=\"font-size:11.5pt;font-family:\" new=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1918","checkdouble":"192600"},{"date":"15:51 02/08","title":"HLV Klopp ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t t\u1eeb t\u00e2n binh Alisson","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/hlv-klopp-tiet-lo-nhung-dieu-dac-biet-tu-tan-binh-alisson.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Alisson, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t t\u1eeb t\u00e2n binh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Alisson t\u1edbi Liverpool v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, HLV Klopp \u0111\u00e3 trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u1ea3 Mignolet v\u00e0 Karius nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh n\u00e0o \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Mignolet ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u00ec Karius l\u1ea1i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t t\u00e2m l\u00fd.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Alisson h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Alisson h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/HLV-Jurgen-Klopp-phat-bieu-ve-Alisson-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Alisson l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nLiverpool \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn, b\u1edfi v\u1eady HLV Klopp kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf\u00a0ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-liverpool-kich-no-bom-tan-alisson-172-191632.html\" target=\"_blank\">Liverpool chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson </span>c\u1ee7a Roma. \u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992, The Kop \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra t\u1edbi 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. S\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua Alisson ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Roma, ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Brazil. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992, h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Liverpool s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Klopp ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t t\u1eeb Alisson</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Alisson, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t t\u1eeb t\u00e2n binh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Klopp phat bieu ve tan binh Alisson\" title=\"HLV Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u00e2n binh Alisson\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/hlv-klopp-tiet-lo-nhung-dieu-dac-biet-tu-tan-binh-alisson.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u00e2n binh Alisson</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho Liverpool, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Alisson. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng khi BL\u0110 chi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u01b0a Alisson v\u1ec1 Anfield. T\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u00fap c\u1eadu \u1ea5y h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch nhanh nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201c\u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn \u1edf c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, Alisson r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00fang gi\u1edd. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 t\u1ecf ra c\u1ea7u ti\u1ebfn. Alisson th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 th\u00f4ng minh, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1 c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cAlisson cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c ngay c\u1ea3 trong nh\u1eefng bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp, ngay c\u1ea3 trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i t\u1eadp trung. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Liverpool\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1917","checkdouble":"192554"},{"date":"16:17 02/08","title":"Tottenham s\u1eafp c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/tottenham-sap-co-tan-binh-dau-tien-tri-gia-30-trieu-bang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tottenham mu\u1ed1n mua Lewis Cook c\u1ee7a Bournemouth \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, \u0111\u00e2y nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Spurs \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tottenham v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e2n binh n\u00e0o \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong s\u1ed1 20 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tham d\u1ef1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19, Tottenham l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng duy nh\u1ea5t ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung n\u00e0o.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tottenham mu\u1ed1n mua Lewis Cook v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tottenham mu\u1ed1n mua Lewis Cook v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/Tottenham-muon-mua-Lewis-Cook-voi-gia-30-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Pochettino v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t t\u00e2n binh n\u00e0o \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi m\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, vi\u1ec7c Spurs kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd b\u1ecb t\u1ee5t l\u1ea1i trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua t\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo The Sun, Tottenham s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng mua m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Spurs kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh khi\u1ebfn NHM c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd kh\u00e1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd, b\u1edfi khi ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi HLV Mauricio Pochettino mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Daniel Levy chi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1eabn c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 Tottenham mua th\u00eam nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c mua s\u1eafm c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t im \u1eafng, kh\u00f4ng \u00edt NHM \u0111ang lo l\u1eafng v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u1ee7a \u201cG\u00e0 tr\u1ed1ng\u201d \u1edf m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Tottenham mu\u1ed1n mua Lewis Cook</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tottenham mu\u1ed1n mua Lewis Cook c\u1ee7a Bournemouth \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, \u0111\u00e2y nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Spurs \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tottenham chi 30 trieu bang mua Lewis Cook\" title=\"Tottenham chi 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Lewis Cook\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/tottenham-sap-co-tan-binh-dau-tien-tri-gia-30-trieu-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Tottenham chi 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Lewis Cook</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Lewis Cook l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Bournemouth. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1997 ra s\u00e2n 29 l\u1ea7n \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 v\u00e0 ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London nh\u1eafm Lewis Cook nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho Dembele. Vi\u1ec7c Victor Wanyama v\u00e0 Harry Winks d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f2n Eric Dier v\u00e0 Moussa Dembele ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau World Cup 2018 c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn Spurs \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBournemouth b\u1ecf ra 7 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Lewis Cook, l\u00fac n\u00e0y h\u1ecd \u0111\u00f2i 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi Bournemouth c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 2 n\u0103m, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1916","checkdouble":"192555"},{"date":"16:08 02/08","title":"Koscielny ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m r\u1eddi Arsenal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/9/koscielny-tiet-lo-thoi-diem-roi-arsenal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Rudiger ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 5. Nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a HLV Emery trong hi\u1ec7p hai \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Arsenal l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Lacazette ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>Chelsea c\u1ea7n Emerson h\u01a1n bao gi\u1edd h\u1ebft\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn c\u00e2n s\u1ee9c Chelsea 1-1 Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn c\u00e2n s\u1ee9c Chelsea 1-1 Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/Diem-nhan-sau-tran-chien-can-suc-Chelsea-1-1-Arsenal-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Emerson h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 c\u1ee7a Sarri h\u01a1n Alonso</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n sang ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Sarri. H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y gi\u00fap h\u1ecd x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc h\u01a1n. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u0169ng n\u1ea3y sinh khi Marcos Alonso kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u00edch nghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 Emerson Palmieri \u0111ang tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 cho su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh b\u00ean h\u00e0nh lang tr\u00e1i c\u1ee7a Chelsea m\u00f9a t\u1edbi. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, ch\u01b0a r\u00f5 HLV Sarri \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o v\u1ec1 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil khi anh ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0o \u1edf gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nAlonso l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi gia nh\u1eadp s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge. Nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha trong h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng m\u1edbi l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Arsenal \u0111\u1eb7t ra m\u1ed9t c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi l\u1edbn cho Sarri v\u1ec1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Alonso khi m\u00e0 Bellerin v\u00e0 Mkhitaryan li\u00ean t\u1ee5c t\u00ecm ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1ch l\u00e0m m\u01b0a l\u00e0m gi\u00f3 v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda khung th\u00e0nh Chelsea.</div>\r\n<h2>Guendouzi th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng l\u1edbn\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Matteo Guendouzi\" title=\"Matteo Guendouzi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/170354-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Matteo Guendouzi c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Matteo Guendouzi l\u00e0 t\u00e2n binh m\u1edbi gia nh\u1eadp Arsenal h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. V\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb 19 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Arsenal, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Emery trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ee7 90 ph\u00fat tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGuendouzi th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi \u0111\u1ea3m tr\u00e1ch v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 l\u00f9i s\u00e2u. Anh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean l\u00f9i v\u1ec1 nh\u1eadn b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 khi n\u00e0o nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 l\u01a1 l\u00e0 n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGuendouzi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i hay nh\u1ea5t b\u00ean ph\u00eda Arsenal \u0111\u00eam qua. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ecdc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 thay \u0111\u1ed5i tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i t\u1eeb ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 sang t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Guendouzi l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng nh\u00ecn chung, sao tr\u1ebb 19 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i Premier League. C\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Lorient c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh, qua \u0111\u00f3 n\u00e2ng cao kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u1eef b\u00f3ng n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n s\u1ed1ng s\u00f3t qua nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Premier League.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-diem-sang-toi-nhin-tu-chien-thang-cua-arsenal-truoc-chelsea-172-192524.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u00e1ng t\u1ed1i nh\u00ecn t\u1eeb chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Arsenal tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Petr Cech ch\u01a1i xu\u1ea5t th\u1ea7n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cech\" title=\"Cech\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/170417-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Cech c\u1ea3n c\u00fa penalty quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00fap Arsenal chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi S\u00e9c \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ea1o ra th\u00eam m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eddi khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169. Anh c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t pha \u0111\u1ed5 ng\u01b0\u1eddi xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n Alvaro Morata ghi b\u00e0n n\u1edbi r\u1ed9ng c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t cho Chelsea tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m penalty \u1edf ph\u00fat 15. Sau \u0111\u00f3, Cech c\u0169ng c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00fa s\u00fat penalty c\u1ee7a Loftus-Cheek \u0111\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1eeb kh\u00e1 s\u1edbm sau m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 h\u1edb h\u00eanh c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u01b0ng l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng 36 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 m\u1ea5t tinh th\u1ea7n m\u00e0 ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng ch\u01a1i t\u1ef1 tin h\u01a1n. V\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a Cech c\u0169ng mang l\u1ea1i cho Arsenal nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i \u00edch kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111ong \u0111\u1ebfm khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u1ea3i b\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb nh\u01b0 Cech l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o c\u0169ng m\u01a1 \u01b0\u1edbc.</div>\r\n<h2>Morata l\u1ea1i \u0111em c\u01a1n \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ebfn cho Sarri\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Morata\" title=\"Morata\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/170506-4.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Morata b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m penalty</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Alvaro Morata \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e1ng qu\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal. V\u00e0 s\u1ef1 thi\u1ebfu \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh khi \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 HLV Sarri c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i lo l\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft HLV Sarri r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n \u0111em ch\u00e2n s\u00fat h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u Gonzalo Higuain \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia l\u00e3o luy\u1ec7n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd c\u0169ng mong mu\u1ed1n h\u1ed3i sinh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u0103n b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Morata.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u1eabu v\u1eady, Morata li\u00ean t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m n\u1ea3n l\u00f2ng \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m thi\u1ebfu \u0111i s\u1ef1 b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o. Anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Cech tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t 11m v\u00e0 c\u0169ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ec7 trong nh\u1eefng pha \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi khung th\u00e0nh Arsenal.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ef1 thi\u1ebfu \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00e0 Morata th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Arsenal m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0 Inter tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 cho th\u1ea5y Chelsea kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u00f4ng c\u1eady v\u00e0o c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0m b\u00e0n t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n th\u00ec Sarri kh\u00f3 tr\u1ee5 l\u1ea1i Chelsea l\u00e2u d\u00e0i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem video tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Chelsea 1-1 Arsenal:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/2/Arsenal-vs-Chelsea_mp4_Output_1.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1915","checkdouble":"192556"},{"date":"16:05 02/08","title":"3 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c M.U ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh ngay trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/3-thuong-vu-chuyen-nhuong-co-the-duoc-mu-hoan-thanh-ngay-trong-tuan-nay.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U \u0111ang l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1 thu h\u00fat s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a NHM Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf tr\u00ean kh\u1eafp th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi trong th\u1eddi gian qua. V\u00e0 li\u1ec7u HLV Mourinho s\u1ebd mang v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t n\u00e0o trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y?</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y 10 ng\u00e0y n\u1eefa, TTCN c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea1i Anh s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda. Kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi n\u0103m, theo quy \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c L\u0110B\u0110 Anh ban h\u00e0nh, th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/2019 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda v\u00e0o l\u00fac 17h00 ng\u00e0y 9/8 (gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng), tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u 1 tu\u1ea7n, thay v\u00ec k\u00e9o d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n ch\u00f3t \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u00e0y 31/8 nh\u01b0 trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0 t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edbm t\u1eadp trung ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 cho CLB. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c TTCN \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda s\u1edbm, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u1eb7t ra nh\u1eefng th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf cho nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 Man United trong vi\u1ec7c tr\u00e1nh b\u1ecb c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c \u00e9p gi\u00e1.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi M.U l\u00fac n\u00e0y, sau c\u00e1c th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng g\u1ed3m Fred, Diogo Dalot v\u00e0 Lee Grant, HLV Jose Mourinho v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Old Trafford m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho s\u1ebd thanh l\u00fd g\u1ea5p m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 'ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1eeba' trong th\u1eddi gian n\u00e0y. V\u1eady \u0111\u00e2u s\u1ebd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh ngay trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y?</p>\r\n<h2>3. Matteo Darmian</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"3 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"3 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/3-thuong-vu-chuyen-nhuong-MU-co-the-hoan-tat-trong-tuan-nay-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng \u1edf c\u1ea3 Anh v\u00e0 Italia \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Matteo Darmian s\u1ebd chia tay M.U ngay trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia ch\u1ec9 ra s\u00e2n v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 17 tr\u1eadn, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 8 tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i Premier League.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Mourinho tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng, Matteo Darmian c\u0169ng b\u00e0y t\u1ecf nguy\u1ec7n v\u1ecdng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra \u0111i v\u00e0 Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y. Ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t CLB nh\u01b0 Juventus, Inter v\u00e0 AC Milan \u0111\u1ec1u b\u00e0y t\u1ecf nguy\u1ec7n v\u1ecdng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mua l\u1ea1i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean l\u00fac n\u00e0y, Inter \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 Sime Vrsaljko, Juve c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Joao Cancelo c\u00f2n AC Milan c\u00f9ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao M.U. T\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1eebng Darmian s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u1edf l\u1ea1i Old Trafford th\u00eam 6 th\u00e1ng n\u1eefa th\u00ec m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y CLB Napoli \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00eca tay ra v\u1edbi anh. V\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 b\u00e1o s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra ngay trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<h2>2. Marcos Rojo</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"trung ve Marcos Rojo\" title=\"trung ve Marcos Rojo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/18/everton-duoc-khuyen-tranh-xa-marcos-rojo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a MU \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e1 ch\u1eadt ch\u1ed9i v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7n di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Chris Smalling, Phil Jones, Eric Bailly hay Victor Lindelof, Marcos Rojo \u0111ang c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i gia nh\u1eadp Manchester United t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2014 v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 16 tri\u1ec7u B\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 h\u01a1n 100 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \"Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf\" v\u00e0 t\u1eebng l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch t\u1ea1i UEFA Europa League. Tuy nhi\u00ean, anh v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y \u00eam \u1ea3 khi ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n 12 l\u1ea7n tr\u00ean t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 Marcos Rojo \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0a Argentina v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng song \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c HLV Mourinho gi\u1eef anh \u1edf l\u1ea1i.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1c b\u00e1o c\u00e1o g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y cho th\u1ea5y Everton \u0111ang th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i. Theo \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e1 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, M.U c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd thu v\u1ec1 kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Anh n\u1ebfu chia tay c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<h2>1. Toby Alderweireld</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alderweireld\" title=\"Alderweireld\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/12/Chuyen-nhuong-Tottenham-he-2018-Kho-quen-roi,-suong-khong-chiu-duoc!-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111ang g\u1ea5p r\u00fat chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Toby Alderweireld, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i. T\u1eeb l\u00e2u HLV Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc cho \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c Eric Bailly. V\u00e0 Toby Alderweireld l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u01b0a th\u00edch c\u1ee7a anh.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo tin t\u1eeb gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, l\u00fac n\u00e0y HLV Mourinho \u0111ang \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd t\u1edbi hai ng\u00f4i sao Maguire v\u00e0 Alderweireld. Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Leicester \u0111ang 'h\u00e9t gi\u00e1' r\u1ea5t cao cho Maguire, Alderweireld \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u1ea1i l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn th\u00edch h\u1ee3p cho Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 t\u1edbi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Anh cho h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00f2n 2 n\u0103m trong h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00f3 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 l\u1eabn kinh nghi\u1ec7m nh\u01b0 ng\u00f4i sao tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9, \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i con s\u1ed1 qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M.U s\u1ebd d\u00f9ng ti\u1ec1n b\u00e1n Darmian v\u00e0 Rojo \u0111\u1ec3 mua Alderweireld, tuy nhi\u00ean s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o trong s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 M.U chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Tottenham ch\u01b0a ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chuyen-nhuong-mu-hot-nhat-ngay-0208-172-192540.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/chuyen-nhuong-mu-hot-nhat-ngay-0208.PNG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chuyen-nhuong-mu-hot-nhat-ngay-0208-172-192540.html\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 02/08</span><br>\r\nChuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 \u0111ang ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u00f4i n\u1ed5i, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 02/08.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tu-bo-maguire-va-alderweireld-mu-muon-mua-mina-cua-barca-172-192523.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/11/tu-bo-maguire-va-alderweireld-mu-muon-mua-mina-cua-barca.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tu-bo-maguire-va-alderweireld-mu-muon-mua-mina-cua-barca-172-192523.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! Bom t\u1ea5n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a MU \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018</span><br>\r\nMU mua Yerry Mina l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a HLV Jose Mourinho, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/kovacic-khong-den-mu-vi-mourinho-184-192497.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/2/kovacic-khong-den-mu-vi-mourinho.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/kovacic-khong-den-mu-vi-mourinho-184-192497.html\">Sao Real t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i MU v\u00ec Mourinho</span><br>\r\nTheo truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng Mateo Kovacic quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gia nh\u1eadp Man United v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i do Mourinho x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1914","checkdouble":"192557"},{"date":"17:24 02/08","title":"B\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch n\u00e0y, M.U s\u1ebd t\u1ed1ng kh\u1ee9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u201cc\u1ee7a n\u1ee3\u201d Martial","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/13/mu-muon-doi-martial-lay-lewandowski-cua-bayern.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M.U mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed5i Martial l\u1ea5y Lewandowski c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0110\u1ee9c mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00f2ng HLV Jose Mourinho song g\u1eb7p tr\u1ee5c tr\u1eb7c \u1edf v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 gi\u00e1 c\u1ea3.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bayern mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Martial</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBayern Munich \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi Anthony Martial trong v\u00e0i th\u00e1ng qua. H\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Allianz Arena h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean, trong khi CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n Man United \u0111\u00f2i 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u1edbi nh\u1ea3 Martial th\u00ec Bayern ch\u1ec9 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng tr\u1edf xu\u1ed1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ea3n th\u00e2n M.U c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y ch\u00ecm xu\u1ed3ng qu\u00e1 nhanh. H\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n qu\u00e1 m\u1eb7n m\u00e0 trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Martial sau nh\u1eefng r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i g\u00e2y ra. Trong 2 m\u00f9a d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Jose Mourinho, c\u1ef1u th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean Monaco kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0 th\u00f4ng qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed5i Martial l\u1ea5y Lewandowski c\u1ee7a Bayern h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed5i Martial l\u1ea5y Lewandowski c\u1ee7a Bayern h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/29/MU-muon-doi-Martial-lay-Lewandowski-cua-Bayern-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Martial khi\u1ebfn HLV\u00a0Mourinho r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady v\u1eabn l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7. Martial v\u1eeba t\u1ea1o ra b\u00ea b\u1ed1i khi kh\u00f4ng quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp trung \u0111\u00fang h\u1ea1n sau khi r\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00f3n ch\u00e0o s\u1ef1 ra \u0111\u1eddi c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi con th\u1ee9 2. HLV Mourinho r\u1ea5t b\u1ef1c t\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u00f3i v\u00f4 k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y. Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t 2 tu\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u01a1ng, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ea3u Martial t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Old Trafford c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t m\u1ecbt m\u1edd.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">M.U t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed5i Martial l\u1ea5y Lewandowski</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Mourinho t\u1eeb l\u00e2u \u0111\u00e3 y\u00eau th\u00edch t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Robert Lewandowski. Nh\u00e2n ti\u1ec7n c\u00f3 Bayern \u0111\u1eb7t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1, M.U mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed5i Martial l\u1ea5y Lewandowski c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. Ph\u00eda Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng c\u00e1c th\u00eam m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 mua l\u1ea1i h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 4 n\u0103m c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Ba Lan.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Niem hy vong so mot cua DT Ba Lan, Robert Lewandowski im tieng trong tran dau nay.\" title=\"Ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ba Lan, Robert Lewandowski im ti\u1ebfng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/lewandowski-noi-gi-sau-tran-thua-soc-cua-ba-lan-truoc-senegal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>M.U mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed5i Martial l\u1ea5y Lewandowski</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Bayern, nh\u1eefng Chelsea v\u00e0 Tottenham c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft t\u1edbi Martial. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, M.U kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1ea1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 tin M.U ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c l\u00ean t\u1edbi 500 ngh\u00ecn b\u1ea3ng n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n Lewandowski \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd gia nh\u1eadp. Nh\u01b0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1edbi Bayern tr\u01b0\u1edbc. \u201cH\u00f9m x\u00e1m\u201d c\u00f3 v\u1ebb kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Lewy, song h\u1ecd c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n Martial thay th\u1ebf l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng Franck Ribery \u0111\u00e3 35 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/3-thuong-vu-chuyen-nhuong-co-the-duoc-mu-hoan-thanh-ngay-trong-tuan-nay-187-192557.html\">3 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c M.U ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh ngay trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/mourinho-muon-mu-chieu-mo-bo-doi-cua-real-187-192515.html\">Mourinho mu\u1ed1n M.U chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i c\u1ee7a Real</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/dai-gia-italia-chua-buong-tha-matteo-darmian-172-192507.html\">\u0110\u1ea1i gia Italia ch\u01b0a bu\u00f4ng tha Matteo Darmian</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-bat-ngo-bi-mat-dam-phan-chieu-mo-pogba-180-192489.html\">Barca b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao kh\u1ee7ng MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/btc-icc-to-ra-thong-cam-voi-mourinho-ve-luc-luong-172-192359.html\">BTC ICC t\u1ecf ra th\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m v\u1edbi Mourinho v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1913","checkdouble":"192561"}]}